{"tid":2351524,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[改善速成輸入法] 提升口語常用字排序","createTime":"2021-01-03T09:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T12:57:58.000Z","uid":53673,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"68412a192a82ec25a599e6b9215da440ed3dee0c","tid":2351524,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T09:39:06.000Z","msg":"「嗰」　6下space先搵到<br />\n影響：貪方便用「果」<br />\n建議：提升排序至頭1頁，取代「唁」<br />\n<br />\n「啲」　4下space先搵到<br />\n影響：貪方便用「D」<br />\n建議：提升排序至頭1頁，取代「吆」<br />\n<br />\n「喺」 3下space先搵到<br />\n影響：貪方便用「係」<br />\n建議：提升排序至頭1頁，取代「啖」<br />\n<br />\n「哋」　3下space先搵到<br />\n影響：貪方便用「地」<br />\n建議：提升排序至頭1頁，取代「吁」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>反例</ins><br />\n「唔」　1下space就搵到<br />\n影響：經常被正確使用，使用「5」則會被屌<br />\n建議：keep status quo"},{"pid":"6d84de7a9973b362bc9f78bd01b51086fe811705","tid":2351524,"uid":305548,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"喺同係完全係兩個意思嚟 唔好亂教人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7a3e079f4c4cd0b995c6822a1240d75eead686","tid":2351524,"uid":53673,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6d84de7a9973b362bc9f78bd01b51086fe811705","tid":2351524,"uid":305548,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"喺同係完全係兩個意思嚟 唔好亂教人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T09:45:04.000Z","msg":"就係因為「喺」排太後，啲人貪方便用「係」<br />\n我只係道出我觀察到嘅影響，冇教過人用「係」代替「喺」，有近視可配眼鏡"},{"pid":"dd3d8e1af9fc0674a53723f27ee0c7f4ff86fc8d","tid":2351524,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"「嘅」 5下space先搵到<br />\n影響：貪方便用「既」<br />\n建議：提升排序至頭1頁，取代「巳」"},{"pid":"581d72abea74ee565964742bbce531638f4d8e63","tid":2351524,"uid":65888,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T09:55:55.000Z","msg":"直接上倉頡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812373cfa6790532450aec95748